---
description: React 컴포넌트는 const arrow function으로 작성. Props는 interface/type으로 정의하고 단일 props 객체로 받아 내부에서 destructure. 반환 타입 명시. Standard.js 포맷팅 준수.
globs: ['**/*.tsx']
alwaysApply: true
---

- Define props with `interface`/`type` (e.g. `ButtonProps`). Do not use `prop-types`.
- Components must be exported as `const` arrow functions.
- Component parameter must be a single `props` object: `(props: ButtonProps)` (do not destructure in the parameter list).
- Destructure props inside the component body: `const { ... } = props`
- Explicitly type the component return value (`: JSX.Element`).
- Follow Standard.js formatting: 2-space indentation, single quotes, no semicolons.

Example:

```ts
interface ButtonProps {
  label: string
  onClick?: () => void
}

export const Button = (props: ButtonProps): JSX.Element => {
  const { label, onClick } = props

  return <button onClick={onClick}>{label}</button>
}
```
